short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A user-friendly interface for your digital assets

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Made for anyone and everyone, the MOOI wallet is a friendly, non-custodial crypto wallet for MOOI Network.
It is the native wallet for the MOOI network which supports all the services and tokens that the network has to offer.

MOOI Wallet is a cryptocurrency wallet where you can manage all your assets on the MOOI Network.
Built on the MOOI Network and Klaytn, the MOOI Wallet allows your transactions on the network to be simple, convenient, and secure.

Safely store, trade and manage all your assets within the MOOI Network.
Built for investors and crypto traders, the MOOI Wallet let's you manage your assets easily in the MOOI Network.

Main features
• Non-custodial wallet - possess full control over your tokens.
• Manage your assets built on MOOI and Klaytn in a single wallet.

Discover the easiest and friendliest way to manage your assets for crypto and DeFi on the MOOI Wallet.
